review_text:
if you have entomophobia, arachnaphobia, or even some trypophobia--- DO NOT PLAY THIS GAME. or play with friends and you can stay at base. :)
i still want to recommend this game because it is good. but it is not for me, personally. due to my irrational fear of worms/holes/and spiders, this was kind of a nightmare. 
however, the graphics are very well done. the skill system is cool and i enjoyed doing gardening/cooking. it is a fun little game. just be careful if you're like me lol
